---
import BlankLayout from '../../../layouts/BlankLayout.astro';
import { VideoList } from '../../../components/Video/VideoList';
const post = Astro.props;
post.data = {title: "About Creator"}
---

<BlankLayout {...post.data}>
	<div class="column">
		<section class="content section">
			<h1>Hi there 👋. I'm ajh123 (or Minecraft ICT, or samuelh2005).</h1>
			<p>I'm, a passionate software developer and content creator. I create YouTube videos about various games and my projects. I love gaming and enjoy sharing game-related content with others.</p>
			<p>Please note that "ajh123" is just my GitHub account name. My real name is Samuel Hulme (or Sam Hulme for short).</p>
			
			<h2>✅ What I do</h2>
			<p>I develop software which I publish on GitHub in free time. Everything on this website was made so I can develop my skils in programming and time mangement.</p>

			<h2>❌ What I don't do</h2>
			<p>I don't use Social Media in the way most people do. I have accounts registred for YouTube, Facebook, and LinkedIn but I don't use them (apart from YouTube). My Facebook account is the most active other than YouTube, but I've never posted to it.</p>

			<h2>YouTube</h2>
			<p>I make videos on YouTube, check them out <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@minecraftict">here</a>! It will help my channel a lot if you do.</p>

			<h3>📺 Featured Videos</h3>
			<p>Below is a list of my most recent videos. More can be found on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@minecraftict">my channel</a>.</p>
			<VideoList client:load currentChannelId="UC5ZPyhfbqKT96EmYzANku7Q"/>

			<h2>My Journey</h2>
			<div class="timeline">
				<header class="timeline-header">
					<span class="tag is-medium is-primary">Start</span>
				</header>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker is-image is-32x32 is-icon">🌍</div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<p class="heading">18 Decemeber 2005</p>
						<p>My first hours on this planet.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<header class="timeline-header">
					<span class="tag is-primary">2010</span>
				</header>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker is-image is-32x32 is-icon">🏫</div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<p class="heading">September 2010</p>
						<p>Joined Moorside Primary School.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<header class="timeline-header">
					<span class="tag is-primary">2016</span>
				</header>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker is-image is-32x32 is-icon">📺</div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<p class="heading">April 2016</p>
						<p>I created my YouTube account, <a href="https://github.com/@minecraftict">Minecraft ICT</a>.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<header class="timeline-header">
					<span class="tag is-primary">2017</span>
				</header>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker is-image is-32x32 is-icon">🎉</div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<p class="heading">June 2017</p>
						<p>Finished Moorside Primary School.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker is-image is-32x32 is-icon">🏫</div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<p class="heading">September 2017</p>
						<p>Joined Moorside High School.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<header class="timeline-header">
					<span class="tag is-primary">2018</span>
				</header>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker is-image is-32x32 is-icon">💻</div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<p class="heading">August 2018</p>
						<p>I created my GitHub account, <a href="https://github.com/ajh123">ajh123</a>.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<header class="timeline-header">
					<span class="tag is-primary">2020</span>
				</header>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker is-image is-32x32 is-icon">📑</div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<p class="heading">September 2020</p>
						<p>Enrolled on to GCSE English Language, GCSE English Literature, GCSE Combined Science, GCSE Geography, GCSE History, and GCSE Computer Science.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<header class="timeline-header">
					<span class="tag is-primary">2022</span>
				</header>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker is-image is-32x32 is-icon">🎉</div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<p class="heading">June 2022</p>
						<p>Passed my GCSE English Language, GCSE English Literature, GCSE Combined Science, GCSE Geography, GCSE History, and GCSE Computer Science exams. My grades were 5, 4, 5, 65, 5, 4, and 6 retrospectively.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker is-image is-32x32 is-icon">📑</div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<p class="heading">September 2022</p>
						<p>I started a BTEC National Extended Diploma in Computing in the Future Skils part of Salford City Collage.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<header class="timeline-header">
					<span class="tag is-primary">2023</span>
				</header>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker is-image is-32x32 is-icon">💻</div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<p class="heading">March 2023</p>
						<p>I completed the first stage for the World Skills Web development competition under 5 minutes with a score of 98% (24/25). I had 30 minutes and two attempts to complete it, but I've done it in one attempt.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-header">
					<span class="tag is-medium is-primary">2024</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</BlankLayout>